-- Gazprom Neft Looking at Bid for Hellenic Petroleum, Dyukov Says
-- B y   S t e p h e n   B i e r m a n
-- 2012-04-06T11:00:00Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-06/gazprom-neft-looking-at-bid-for-hellenic-petroleum-dyukov-says.html
OAO Gazprom Neft (SIBN) , the oil producing
arm of  Russia ’s natural-gas monopoly, is considering a bid for
 Hellenic Petroleum SA (ELPE) ,  Greece ’s biggest refiner, Gazprom Neft
Chief Executive Officer Alexander Dyukov said.  The St. Petersburg, Russia-based company, has not made a
decision on whether to bid for the refinery, he said.  Greece plans to sell its stake in Athens-based Hellenic
Petroleum this year.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Stephen Bierman in Moscow at 
